Subject: [PATCH] kernelbase: Implement TzSpecificLocalTimeToSystemTimeEx()

We also reimplement TzSpecificLocalTimeToSystemTime using
TzSpecificLocalTimeToSystemTimeEx.

Signed-off-by: Richard Yao <ryao@gentoo.org>
---
